data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home that sits on a spacious corner lot in Carencro La. Only one owner has had the luxury of calling this beauty home, and has kept it in pristine condition. The interior features a lavish foyer, that leads to the living area, in which you can take advantage of the coziness of the fireplace. The floors are brand new as well! It also showcases a walk-in pantry. The master bathroom is equipped with his/her sinks, a jacuzzi style tub and separate shower. The back patio sets the scene for ultimate relaxation w the covered patio, privacy fence, and lighted sitting area. New fence built in 2021. New roof in 2021 as well! Qualifies for Rural Development 100% financing.
